import React from 'react'
import { AppBar,Toolbar, styled } from '@mui/material'



const Header = styled(AppBar)`
    background: black
`
const Tabs = styled('p')`
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-right:20px;

`


const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Header position='static'>  
        <Toolbar>
            <Tabs>CRUD</Tabs>
            <Tabs>All users</Tabs>
            <Tabs>Add user</Tabs>
        </Toolbar>
    </Header>
  )
}

export default Navbar
